hadiths[57]{hadithnumber,text}:
7329,"Mamar ne hamein Hammam-bin-Munabba se hadis bayan ki, kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kin, unmein se (ye hadis bhi) hai : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Kisraa halaak ho gaya, phir uske baad Kisraa nahi hoga, aur qaisar bhi halaak ho jaeyga phir uske baad koi qaisar nahi hoga aur un donon ke khazaaney Allah ki raah mein taqseem kiye jaengey."
7330,"Hazrat Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab Kisraa halaak ho jaeyga to uske baad koi Kisraa nahi hoga. ( aagey ( unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis ki manind (tarah) zikr kiya."
7331,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur abu-Kamil Jahdari ne kaha : hamein abu-Awana ne Samak-bin-Harab se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : musalmanon ya ( farmaya : ( mominon ki aik jamat aale-Kisraa ke khazaaney ko , jo safaid (Imaarat) mein hai zaroor-zaroor fateh karegi. Quteba ne musalmanon ki (jamat) kaha aur kisi shak ka izhar nahi kiya."
7332,"Shoba ne Samak-bin-Harab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, ( aagey ( abu-Awana ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki."
7333,"Abdul-Azeez-bin-Muhammad ne soor-bin-Zaid-daili se, unhon-ne abu-ghais se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ne aisey Shahar ke barey mein suna hai jiski aik taraf khushki mein hai aur dusri taraf samandar mein hai? unhon (sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen)) ne arz ki, ji haan , Allah ke rasool ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahi hogi yahan tak ke iske khilaf banu-Ishaq mein se sattar (70) hazaar log jihad karengey, wahan pahunch kar wo utrein gey to hathiyaron se jang karengey na teer-andazi karengey, wo kahengey , ''لاالٰہ الا اللہ Allah ki qism اکبر'' to us ( Shahar ( ki aik taraf gir jaeygi. Saur ne kaha : main hi janta hun ke unhon (abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu)) ne wahi (kinara) kaha (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo samandar mein hai. phir wo dusri baar ''لاالٰہ الا اللہ Allah ki qism اکبر'' kahengey to us ( Shahar (ka doosra kinaaraa bhi gir jaeyga. phir wo teesri baar ''لاالٰہ الا اللہ Allah ki qism اکبر'' kahengey to unke liye rasta khul jaeyga aur wo us ( Shahar ( mein dakhil ho jaeinge aur ghaneemat ka maal hasil karengey. jab wo maale-ghanimat taqseem kar rahe hongey to aik cheekhti hui awaz aaeygi jo kahegi : dajjal namudaar ho gaya. chunanche wo (musalman) har cheez chhod dengey aur wapas palat padein gey."
7334,Sulaiman-bin-Bilal ne kaha : hamein soor-bin-Zaid daili ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
7335,"Muhammad-bin-Bashir ne kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : yahood tum se jang karengey aur tum unhein achi tarah qatl karogey yahan tak ke patthar kahega : aey musalman ! ye Yahudi hai, aagey badh , usko qatl kar."
7336,Yahya ne hamein Ubaidullah se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur apni hadis mein kaha : ye Yahudi mere peechhey hai.
7337,"Umar-bin-Hamza ne kaha : maine Salim ko kehtey huey suna : hamein Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum aur yahood aapas mein jang karogey, yahan tak ke patthar kahega : aey musalman ! ye mere peechhey aik Yahudi hai, aagey badh , usey qatl kar de."
7338,"ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Yahudi tum se jang karengey (aakhirkaar) tumhen un par tasallut ata kar diya jaeyga, yahan tak ke patthar (bhi) kahega : aey musalman ! ye Yahudi mere peechhey hai, usko qatl kar do."
7339,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahi hogi, yahan tak ke musalman yahudiyon ke khilaf jang ladein gey aur musalman unko qatl karengey. yahan tak ke Yahudi darakht ya patthar ke peechhey chhipey ga aur patthar ya darakht kahega : aey musalman ! aey Allah ke bandey ! mere peechhey ye aik Yahudi hai aagey badh , usko qatl kar de, siwaey gharqad ke darakht ke (wo nahi kahega) kyonke wo yahood ka darakht hai."
7340,"abul-Ahwas aur abu-Awana donon ne Samak se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir-bin-samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : qiyamat se pahley kai kazzaab (jhoote) hongey. abul-Ahwas ki hadis mein unhon ( abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ( ne mazeed kaha ke maine unse puchha : kya aap ne ye ( baat ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni? unhon-ne kaha : haan."
7341,"aur ibne-Musanna aur ibne-Bashar ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Samak se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki. Samak ne kaha : maine apne bhai ko kehtey huey suna ke Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : un ( jhooton ( se bach kar raho."
7342,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahi hogi, yahan tak ke dajjaalon aur kazzaabon (jhooton) ko bheja jaeyga jo tees ke qareeb hongey. unmein se har aik dawa karta hoga ke wo Allah ka rasool hai."
7343,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki, magar unhon-ne kaha : yahan tak ke wo (shaitan ki taraf se) maboos bin kar (bhejey hue) aaeingey."
7354,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki ke Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne unhein bataya , unhein Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath chand logon mein ibne-Sayyaad ke paas gaey yahan tak ke usey bani-maghaala ke qil'ey ke paas ladkon ke sath kheltey huey dekha un dinon ibne-Sayyaad jawaani ke qareeb tha. usko khabar na hui yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski peeth par apna hath maara. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se puchha ke kya to is baat ki gawahi deta hai ke main Allah Taala ka rasool hun? ibne-Sayyaad ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf dekha aur kaha ke main gawahi deta hun ke tum ummiyeenn ke rasool ho (ummi kehtey hain un-padh aur be-taleem ko). phir ibne-Sayyaad ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke tum is baat ki gawahi detey ho ke main Allah Taala ka rasool hun? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is baat ka kuchh jawab na diya? (aur us se musalman honey ki darkhaast na ki kyonke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iske musalman honey se maayoos ho gaey aur aik riwayat mein saad mohmila se yani Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko laat se maara) aur farmaya ke main Allah par aur uske rasulon par imaan laya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se puchha ke tujhey kya dikhai deta hai? wo bola ke mere paas kabhi sachcha aata hai aur kabhi jhoota. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tera kaam gad-bad ho gaya (yani mila-jula haq aur baatil donon se). phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine tujh se poochhney ke liye aik baat dil mein chhipaai hai. ibne-Sayyaad ne kaha ke wo dukkha ( dhuaan ( hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke zaleel ho, to apni qadr se kahan badh sakta hai? saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! mujhey chhodiye mein iski gardan maarta hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar ye wahi (yani dajjal) hai to to usko mar na sakega aur agar ye wo (dajjal) nahi hai to tujhey iska maarna behtar nahi hai."
7355,"Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey hain is (pichhle waqiey) ke baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Hazrat Ubai-ibne-Ka'b Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) khajooron ke us baagh mein gaey jis mein ibne-Sayyaad tha, baagh mein dakhil honey ke baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khajooron ke tanon ki aad mein honey lagey taake us se pahley ke ibne-Sayyaad aapko dekhey aap uski koi baat sun lein, wo bistar par aik narm chadar main (usey odh kar leta) hua tha. uske andar se uski gungunaahat ki awaz aa rahi thi. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khajoor ke darakhton ki aad ley rahe they, to ibne-Sayyaad ki maan ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh liya aur wo ibne-Sayyaad se kehney lagi saaf !  aur ye ibne-Sayyaad ka naam tha. ye Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (aaey) hain. ibne-Sayyaad uchhal kar khada ho gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar wo usko (usi haalat mein) chhod deti to wo (apna mamla) waazeh kar deta."
7368,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hamein hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Shoba ne abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Rabai-bin-Hirash se unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dajjal ke barey mein, (farmaya) be-shak uske sath  pani hoga aur aag hogi uski aag (asl mein) thanda pani hoga aur uska pani aag hogi to tum log (dhokey mein) halaak na ho jana."
7523,"Mamar ne Hammam-bin-Munabba se hadis bayan ki, kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, phir unhon-ne kai hadison zikr kin, unmein se (eik hadis) ye hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Bani-Israeel se kaha gaya : (Shahar ke) darwazey mein sajda kartey huey jao aur kaho : hatta (hamein bakhsh de) ham tumhari khataein bakhsh dengey, unhon-ne (iske) ulat kiya, chunanche wo apne chootdon ke bal ghaseet'tey huey darwazey se dakhil huey aur unhon-ne (hatta ke bajaey) hamein baali mein daana chahiye kaha."
7524,"ibne-Shahab se riwayat hai, kaha : mujhey Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat se pahley aap ki wafat tak lagaataar wahi nazil farmai aur jis din aap ki wafat hui us din sabse zyada wahi aai."
7525,"Sufiyan ne Qais-bin-Muslim se aur unhon-ne taariq-bin-shahaab se riwayat ki ke yahudiyon ne Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : aap log (musalman) aik aisi aayat padhtey hain ke agar wo aayat hamarey yahaan nazil hoti to ham us din ko eid bana letey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main janta hun, wo aayat kis jagah aur kis din nazil hui thi aur jis waqt wo nazil hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kahan they. ye aayat Arfa (ke maqam) par nazil hui thi aur us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maidan Arafaat mein they. Sufiyan ne kaha mujhey shak hai ke (hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye bhi kaha tha) Juma ka din tha ya nahi? unki murad is aayat se thi : ''aaj maine tumharey liye tumhara Deen mukammal kar diya aur tum par apni nemat poori kar di.''"
7526,"Abdullah-bin-Idris ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Qais-bin-Muslim se aur unhon-ne taariq-bin-shahaab se riwayat ki, kaha : yahood ne Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : agar ye aayat ham yahudiyon ki jamat par nazil hoti : ''aaj maine tumhare liye tumhara Deen mukammal kar diya aur tum par apni nemat ka itmaam (khatma) kar diya aur tumharey liye Islam ko bataur Deen pasand kar liya.''  hamein pata hota ke wo kis din nazil hui hai to ham us din ko eid qarar detey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main wo din aur wo ghadi jis mein ye aayat utari thi, aur iske nuzool ke waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kis jagah they (sab kuchh ( janta hun. ye (aaya ( Muzdalfa ki raat (aaney wali thi, tab) utri thi, aur (us waqt) ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Arafaat mein they."
7527,"abu-Umais ne Qais-bin-Muslim se aur unhon-ne taariq-bin-shahaab se riwayat ki, kaha : yahudiyon mein se aik shakhs Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur kehney laga : ameerul-momeneen ! aap ki kitab mein aik aisi aayat hai, aap usey padhtey hain, agar wo ham yahudiyon par nazil hui hoti to ham us din ko eid qarar detey. aap (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha : wo kon si aayat hai? usne kaha : ''aaj maine tumharey liye tumhara Deen mukammal kar diya aur tum par apni nemat tamam kar di aur tumharey liye Islam ko Deen ke taur par pasand kar liya.'' to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main wo din bhi janta hun jis mein ye nazil hui wo jagah bhi jahan ye nazil hui. ye (aayat) Arafaat mein Juma ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par nazil hui thi."
7528,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke farman : agar tumhen khadsha (dar) ho ke tum yateem ladkiyon ke mamley mein insaf nahi kar paogey to un aurton mein se, jo tumhen achchhi lagein do-do, teen-teen, char-char se nikah kar lo ke barey mein sawal kiya to unhon-ne kaha : mere bhaanjey ! ye us yateem ladki ke barey mein hai jo apne wali ki kifaalat (bharan-poshan) mein hoti hai uske (virasat ke taur par) maal mein uskey sath Sharik hoti hai to uske wali (chacha-zaad waghaira) ko uska maal aur jamaal donon pasand hotey hain aur uska wali chahta hai ke uske mehar mein insaf kiye baghair us se shadi kar ley aur wo bhi usey itna mehar de jitna koi doosra usey dega. chunanche un (logon) ko is baat se rok diya gaya ke wo unke sath shadi karein siwaey-iske ke wo (mehar mein) unse insaf karein aur mehar mein jo sabse uncha tariqa (raaij (laagu)) hai uski pabandi karein aur (agar wo aisa nahi kar saktey to) unhein hukm diya gaya ke un (yateem ladkiyon) ke siwa jo auratein unhein achchhi lagein unse shadi kar lein. Urwa ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : phir logon ne is aayat ke baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (aurton ke hawale se mazeed) malum kiya to izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne (ye aayat ( nazil farmai : ''aur ye aap se aurton ke barey mein malum kartey hain. kahey : Allah tumhen unke barey mein fatwa deta hai aur jo kuchh tum par kitab mein padha jata hai wo un yateem aurton ke barey mein hai jinhein tum wo nahi detey jo unke liye farz kiya gaya hai aur raghbat (dilchaspi) rakhtey ho ke unse nikah kar lo.''  ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : jis baat ka Allah Taala ne zikr farmaya hai ke wo kitab mein tilawat ki jati hai, wo wahi pehli aayat hai jis mein Allah farmata hai : ''agar tumhen khadsha (dar) ho ke tum yateem ladkiyon ke barey mein insaf nahi kar paao gey to (doosri) jo auratein tumhen achchhi lagein unse nikah karo.''  hazrat  Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : aur baad wali aayat mein Allah Taala ke farman : ''aur tum unke nikah se raghbat kartey ho. (ka matlab hai ke) jab tum mein se kisi ki sarparasti mein rehney wali ladki maal aur jamaal mein kam ho to is se (shadi karne se) roo-gardaani (nafarmaani) karnaa, chunanche unse (nikah ki) raghbat (dilchaspi) na honey ki bina par unko mana kiya gaya ke wo jin (yateem ladkiyon) ke maal aur jamaal mein raghbat rakhtey hain unse bhi shadi na karein siwaey-iske ke (mehar mein) insaf se kaam lein.''"
7529,"Saleh ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Urwa ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se Allah tabarak w taala ke farman : aur tumhen khadsha ho ke tum yateem ladkiyon ke barey mein insaf na kar paogey ke barey mein poochha, phir Zohri se Yunus ki riwayat ki hui hadis ke mutabiq bayan kya aur uske aakhir mein mazeed kaha : agar wo maal aur jamaal mein kam ho to tumharey unse earaaz karne ki bina par."
7530,"abu-Usama ne kaha : hamein Hisham ne apne walid ( Urwa ( se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke farman : agar tumhen khadsha ho ke tum yateem ladkiyon ke barey mein adl nahi kar paogey ke mutaalliq riwayat ki) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : ye ( aayat ( aisey aadmi ke barey mein nazil hui jiske paas koi yateem ladki ho wo uska wali aur waaris ho. us ladki ka maal (main bhi haq) ho us (ladki ke mafaad) ke liye koi shakhs jhagda karne wala bhi na ho to wo aadmi us ladki ke maal ki bina par uski kahin aur shadi na karey aur usey nuqsan pahunchaaey aur us se bura sulook karey to us (Allah) ne farmaya : agar tumhen andesha hai ke tum yateem ladkiyon ke mamley mein insaf na kar paogey to (doosri ( jo auratein tumhen achi lagein unhein se nikah karo. wo ( Allah ( farmata hai. (doosri aurton se nikah kar lo ( jo maine tumharey liye (nikah ke tareeq par) halal ki hain aur us (ladki) ko chhod do jis ko tum nuqsan pahuncha rahe ho."
7531,"Abda bin Sulaiman ne Hisham se unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke farman : jo kitab mein un yateem aurton ke barey mein tilawat ki jati hai jinko tum wo (mehar) nahi detey jo unke haq mein farz hai aur unke nikah se raghbat kartey ho. ke barey mein riwayat bayan ki. (Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : ye aisi yateem ladki ke barey mein nazil hui jo kisi aadmi ke paas hoti, uske maal mein uske sath Sharik hoti aur wo us se (shadi karne se) kinara-kashi karta hai aur is baat ko bhi na-pasand karta hai ke kisi aur ke sath uski shadi karey aur us (shakhs) ko apne maal mein Sharik karey to wo usey waisey hi bithaaey rakhta hai na khud us se shadi karta hai aur na kisi aur se uski shadi karta hai."
7532,"abu-Usama ne kaha : hamein Hisham ne apne walid se khabar di unhon-ne izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke farman : aur ye log aap se aurton ke barey mein sawal kartey hain kahey Allah tumhen unke barey mein fatwa deta hai. mukammal aayat ke barey mein Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ye aisi yateem ladki (ke barey mein) hai jo kisi aadmi ke paas hoti hai. shayad wo aisi bhi hoti hai ke wo iske maal mein yahan tak ke khajoor ke darakhton mein bhi iske sath Sharik hoti hai, wo khud bhi us se ru-gardaani karta yani us se shadi karne se aur kisi aur ke sath uski shadi karke us (shakhs) ko apne maal mein Sharik karne ko bhi pasand nahi karta to wo usey waisey hi rehney deta hai."
7533,Abda bin Sulaiman ne Hisham (bin Urwa ( se unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke farman : aur jo faqeer ho wo dastoor ke mutabiq kha ley ke mutaalliq riwayat ki (Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) farmaya : ye aayat yateem ke maal ke aisey mutwalli ke barey mein nazil hui hai jo uski nigahdaasht karta hai aur usko sanwaarta (badhata) hai ke agar wo zarurat mand hai to usmein se ( khud bhi) kha sakta hai.
7534,"abu-Usama ne kaha : hamein Hisham ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se us azz-w-jall ke farman : aur jo shakhs ghani ho wo ijtinab karey aur jo shakhs zarurat mand ho. wo urf aur riwaaj ke mutabiq kha ley ke mutaalliq riwayat ki (Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : ye (aayat) yateem ke sar-parast ke mutaalliq nazil hui ke jab wo mohtaaj ho to iske maal mein se Maruf tareeqey se utna ley sakta hai jitna apna maal (istemal karta tha.)"
7535,ibne-Numair ne kaha : hamein Hisham ne isi sanad ke sath ( yahi ( hadis bayan ki.
7536,"Urwa ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se us (Allah) azz-w-jall ke farman : jab kaafir tum par chadh aaey tumharey uper ki taraf se aur tumharey nichey ki taraf se aur jab aankhen phir gain aur dil munh ko aaney lagey ke mutaalliq riwayat ki, ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) farmaya : ye khandaq ke roz hua tha."
7537,"Abda bin Sulaiman ne kaha : hamein Hisham (ibne-Urwa) ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se ( aayat ( : aur agar koi aurat apne khawind ki taraf se be raghbati yaaro gardaani ka andesha mehsus karey mukammal aayat ke barey mein riwayat ki) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) farmaya : ye aayat us aurat ke mutaalliq nazil hui thi. jo kisi mard ke nikah mein ho. uski sohbat mein lamba arsa bait gaya ho wo usey talaaq dena chahey to wo ( aurat ( kahey mujhey talaaq na 2 apne paas rakho . tum meri taraf se ( mere waajibaat se) bariuzzimma ho, chunanche ye aayat nazil hui."
7538,abu-Usama ne kaha : hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa ne apne walid se bayan kya unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se us (Allah ( azz-w-jall ke farman : agar koi aurat apne khawind ki taraf se be raghbati ya ru-gardaani ka andesha mehsus karne ke mutaalliq riwayat ki) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne) farmaya : ye ( aayat (us aurat ke mutaalliq nazil hui jo (muddat se) kisi mard ke yahan ho. (usey andesha ho (ke shayad ab wo us se (apne talluq ko) zyada na karega aur us (aurat) ko uska sath muyassar ho aur aulad ho aur ye na chahey ke wo (mard) usey chhod de to us se keh de ke tum mere mamley main (huqooq zaujiyat se) bariuzzimma ho.
7539,"abu-Muawiya ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujh se Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya bhaanjey! logon ko hukm diya gaya tha ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab ke liye istighfar karein to unhon-ne unko bura kehna shuru kar diya."
7540,abu-Usama ne kaha : hamein Hisham ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
7541,Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Mughira bin Nauman se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Hazrat Saeed-bin-Jubair se riwayat ki kaha : ke ahle-koofa ka us aayat ke barey mein ikhtilaf ho gaya jis shakhs ne kisi momin ko jaan-bojh kar qatl kya uski saza jahannam hai? chunanche main safar karke Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya aur unse us ( aayat (ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne kaha : ye aayat aakhir mein nazil hui phir kisi cheez (Quran ki kisi dusri aayat ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke farman) ne usko mansukh nahi kya.
7542,Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur Nazar-bin-Shumail donon ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki. ibne-Jafar ki riwayat mein hai ye aayat aakhir mein utarne wali aayaton mein utri aur nazar ki riwayat mein hai ye (aayat) yaqinan un aayaton mein se hai jo aakhir mein utrin.
7543,"Mansoor ne Hazrat Saeed-bin-Jubair se riwayat ki kaha : mujh se Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Abza ne kaha : ke main (unke liye) Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se un 2 aayaton ke mutaalliq malum karun : aur jo shakhs jaan-bojh kar kisi momin ko qatl kar de, uski saza jahannam hai aur wo usmein hamesha rahega. maine unse puchha to unhon-ne kaha : usko kisi cheez ne mansukh nahi kya aur us aayat ke mutaalliq (poochha) aur jo log Allah ke siwa kisi aur ki ibadat nahi kartey aur na haq ke baghair kisi shakhs ko qatl kartey hain jiske qatl ko Allah ne haram kya hai. to unhon-ne kaha : mushrekeen ke barey mein nazil hui hai."
7544,"abu-Muawiya Sheban ne Mansoor bin Motamir se unhon-ne Saeed bin Juber se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ye aayat : jo log Allah ke sath kisi aur maabood ko nahi pukaartey se lekar zillat ke aalim mein (hamesha rahega) tak Makka mein nazil hui. mushrikon ne kaha : hamein Islam kis baat ka fayda dega. jabke ham Allah ke sath (doosron ko) Sharik bhi thehra chukey hain aur Allah ki haram karda jaanon ko qatl bhi kar chukey hain aur fawaahish ka irtikaab bhi kar chukey hain? is par Allah Taala ne (ye aayat ( nazil farmai : siwaey us shakhs ke jisne tauba ki eman ley aaya aur nek amal kiye aayat ke aakhiri hissey tak. unhon-ne (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : lekin jo shakhs Islam mein dakhil ho gaya aur usko samajh liya phir us ne (jan-boojhkar kisi momin ko) qatl kya to uske liye koi tauba nahi."
7545,"Abdullah-bin Hashim aur Abdur-Rehman bin Bishr abdi ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed qattaan ne ibne-Juraij se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Qasim bin abi baza ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya jis shakhs ne kisi momin ko jan-boojhkar qatl kar diya uske liye tauba (ki gunjaaish) hai? unhon-ne kaha : nahi ( Saeed-bin-Jubair ne) kaha : phir maine unke samney sura furqan ki ye aayat tilawat ki. wo log jo Allah ke siwa kisi aur maabood ko nahi pukaartey aur kisi jaan ko jisey Allah ne haram kya hai haq ke baghair qatl nahi kartey. padhi. aayat ke aakhir tak unhon-ne kaha : ye Makki aayat hai usko us madni aayat ne mansukh kar diya : aur jo kisi momin ko umda qatl kar de to uski saza jahannam hai wo usmein hamesha rahega. ibne-Hashim ki riwayat mein hai : to maine unke samney ye aayat padhi jo sura furqan mein hai : siwaey iske jisne tauba ki."
7546,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba, Harun bin-Abdullah aur abd bin Humaid ne hamein hadis bayan ki, abd ne kaha : hamein khabar di aur dusron ne kaha : hamein hadis bayan ki, Jafar bin Aun ne unhon-ne kaha : hamein abu Umais ne Abdul Majid bin Suhel se khabar di. unhon-ne Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se farmaya : kya tum jantey ho ke Quran Majeed ki aakhiri sura jo yakbaargi mukammal nazil hui kon si hai? maine kaha : ji haan. ( إ ( ِذَا جَاء نَصْرُ اللَّهِ وَالْفَتْحُ ( unhon-ne farmaya : tum ne sach kaha, aur ibne-Abi-Sheba ki riwayat mein hai. tum jantey ho ke kon si sura hai aur aakhiri (ka lafz) nahi kaha."
7547,abu-Muawiya ne kaha : hamein abu Umais ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki aur kaha : aakhiri sura aur unhon-ne (rawi ka naam letey huey) Abdul-Majeed (se marwi) kaha : aur ibne-Suhail (Abdul Majid bin Suhail) nahi kaha.
7548,"Ata ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : musalmanon mein se kuchh log aik shakhs ko miley jo bakriyon ke aik chhotey se rewad mein tha us ne (unko dekh kar) kaha : Assalaamualaikum. to (iske bawajood) unhon-ne usko pakda usey qatl kya aur bakriyon ka wo chhota sa rewad ley liya. to ye aayat utri : aur usey jo tum se salam kahey ye mat kaho ke tum momin nahi ho. (aur Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne us ( السلم ( ko السلام padha ( ."
7549,Abu-Ishaq se riwayat hai kaha : maine Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : Ansar jab Haj karke wapas aatey to gharon main (darwazon ke bajaey) unke pichhwadey hi se dakhil hotey Ansar mein se aik shakhs aaya aur apne darwazey se (ghar ke andar ( dakhil hua to uske barey mein is par baatein ki gain to ye aayat utri : aur ye koi neki nahi ke tum gharon ke andar unke pichhwaadon se aao.
7550,Aun bin-Abdullah ke walid se riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : hamarey Islam laney aur ham par us aayat ke zariey se Allah Taala ke itaab ke darmyan char saal se zyada ka waqfa nahi tha : kya eman laney walon ke liye abhi ye waqt nahi aaya ke unke dil Allah ko yad kartey huey gid-gidaaein.
7551,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : (jaahili daur mein) aik aurat barahna ho kar Baitullah ka tawaaf karti thi aur kehti thi : kon mujhey tawaaf karne wala aik kapda dega? ke wo usko apni sharmgah par daal ley , aur (ye sher ( kehti : aaj ( badan ka ( kuchh hissey ya poorey ka pura khul jaeyga aur is mein se jo bhi khul gaya main usey (dekhna kisi ke liye) halal nahi kar rahi. is par ye aayat nazil hui : har Namaz ke waqt apni zeenat ley lo."
7552,"abu-Muawiya ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne abu Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Abdullah-bin-Ubai salool apni aik baandi se kehta tha : ja aur (bazariey badkaari) hamarey liye kuchh kama kar la, to izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne (ye aayat) nazil farmai : aur apni laundiyon ko badkaari par na uksaao (khususan) agar wo paakdaaman rehna chahti hon taake tum duniya ki zindagi ka saazo-saamaan hasil karo aur jo koi unhein majbur karega to Allah Taala unke majbur kiye janey ke baad unke liye bada bakhshney waala, bada raham karne wala hai."
7553,"abu-Awana ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu Sufiyan se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Abdullah-bin-Ubai ibne-Salool ki aik baandi thi, uska naam Musaika tha, aur dusri ( baandi ( ko Umaima kaha jata tha. wo un donon se (zabardasti) zina karaana chahta tha. un donon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein is baat ki shikayat ki to izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne aayat : aur apni naujawaan laundiyon ko badkaari par na uksaao agar wo paakdaaman rehna chahti hun. us ( Allah (ke farman : bada bakhshney waala, hamesha raham karne wala hai. tak nazil farmai."
7554,"Abdullah-bin-Idris ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne abu Mamar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke us farman ke mutaalliq riwayat ki : wo log jinhein ye (kaafir) pukaartey hain wo khud apne rab ki taraf waseela talash kartey hain ke unmein se kon zyada nazdeek hoga. (ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : jinon ki aik jamat musalman ho gaee thi aur (is se pahley) unki puja ki jati thi, to jo unki ibadat kya kartey they, unki ibadat par qaaim rahe jabke jinon ki ye jamat khud Islam ley aai."
7556,Shoba ne Sulaiman (Aamash) se isi sanad ke sath yahi riwayat ki.
7558,"abu Bishr ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se riwayat ki, kaha : ke maine saiyedna Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke sura Tauba ? unhon-ne kaha ke sura Tauba? aur kaha ke balke wo sura to zaleel karne wali hai aur fazeehat karne wali hai) kaafiron aur munaafiqon ki) . is sura mein barabar utartaa raha ke ''aur unmein se'' ''aur unmein se'' yahan tak ke munafiq log samjhey ke koi baqi na rahega jiska zikr is sura mein na kya jaeyga maine kaha ke sura al-Anfaal? unhon-ne kaha ke wo sura to badr ki ladai ke barey mein hai (is mein maale-ghanimat ke ehkaam mazkoor hain). maine kaha ke sura Hashr? unhon-ne kaha ke wo bani-Nazeer (ke anjam) ke barey mein nazil hui."
7559,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne abu-Hayyan se, unhon-ne Shabi se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke member par) khadey ho kar) khutba diya, Allah Taala ki hamdo-sanaa bayan ki, phir kaha : iske baad : suno ! sharab ki hurmat nazil hui, jis din wo nazil hui (us waqt) wo panch chizon se banti thi. gehun, jo, khushk khajoor, angoor aur shehad se, khamr wo hai jo aql ko dhanp ley. aur logo! teen cheezein aisi hain jinke mutaalliq main shiddat se chahta hun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke barey mein hamein aur zyada saaf-saaf bataya hota : dada aur kalaala ki meeraas aur sood ke abwaab mein se chand abwaab."
7560,"ibne-Idrees ne kaha : hamein abu-Hayyan ne Shabi se hadis bayan ki. unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke member par farmatey huey suna : hamd w sana ke baad, logo! sharab ki hurmat nazil hui to wo panch chizon se banai jati thi, angoor , khajoor , shehad , gandam aur jo se aur khamr (sharab) wo hai jo aql ko dhaank de. logo! teen cheezein aisi hain jinke mutaalliq main chahta tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein aur zyada wazahat se farma detey : dada aur kalaala ki meeraas aur sood ki Suraton mein se chand sooratein."
7561,"Ismail bin-Ulaih aur Esa-bin-Yonus donon ne abu-Hayyan se isi sanad ke sath un donon ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki, albatta ibne-Ulaih ki hadis mein hai : angoor, jis tarah ibne-Idrees ne kaha hai. aur Esa ki riwayat mein kishmish hai. jis tarah ibne-Mus-hir ne kaha hai."
7562,"Hushaim ne abu Hashim se, unhon-ne abu Mujliz se aur unhon-ne Qais-bin Ibad se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ko qism kha kar kehtey huey suna ke) aayat ( : ye 2 jhagadney waley hain jinhoney apne rab ke mamley mein jhagda kya. un logon ke mutaalliq nazil hui jinhoney badr ke din mubaarzat (ru-dar-ru seedhi ladai) ki : Hazrat Hamza , Ali aur Ubaida-bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) aur (doosri taraf se) Rabee ke 2 betey : Utba aur Sheba aur Utba ka betaa Waleed."
7563,"Sufiyan ne abu Hashim se, unhon-ne abu mujliz se, unhon-ne Qais-bin Ibad se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ko qism kha kar ye kehtey huey suna : ( هَذَانِ خَصْمَانِ ( ye aayat nazil hui. ( aagey ( Hushaim ki hadis ki tarah hai."
